<P>DISSERTATIONS ON THE NATURE AND EFFECT OF CHRISTIAN BAPTISM, CHRISTIAN COMMUNION, AND RELIGIOUS WAITING UPON GOD.</P>
<P>By JOSEPH PHIPPS.</P>
