<P>REASONS FOR THE NECESSITY OF SILENT WAITING, IN ORDER TO THE SOLEMN WORSHIP OF GOD. TO WHICH ARE ADDED, <HI>SEVERAL QUOT<GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="5 letters">S</HI> FROM ROBERT BARCLAY <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="4 letters">OGY. BY MARY BROOK.</P>
<P>THE SIXTH EDITION.</P>
<P>LONDON, PRINTED: NEW-YORK, RE-PRINTED, BY WILLIAM ROSS, BROAD-STREET, NEAR THE EXCHANGE.</P>
